{"tid":804040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先跑跑下步小妹唔小心賴撚咗屎😂😂","createTime":"2018-09-02T17:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T18:03:48.000Z","uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"18a695931d4a3ab63869299e469116417a83fee4","tid":804040,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:13:00.000Z","msg":"話說我今日去咗keep fit <br />\n咁我跑開街 跑一round 1k 大概20分鐘倒<br />\n咁我跑到一半嘅時候 就覺得有啲便意<br />\n咁我諗住以我咁fit嘅身材（155cm 75kg） 應該可以捱得到返屋企<br />\n我以為我老母生得我咁大個屎忽 <br />\n應該夠肌肉可以谷撚實個屎眼<br />\n之後發現 唔係好撚掂<br />\n就諗住跑去最近嗰個商場嗱嗱聲搞掂佢<br />\n點知入廁所之前經過男廁<br />\n有個好撚靚仔嘅男人 愉望我對巨乳<br />\n雖然我都知小妹身材比較豐滿（155cm 75kg Hcup）<br />\n但係一個靚仔望住自己嘅時候 難不免會心花怒放<br />\n就係呢一刻我失手左<br />\n唔小心放撚左個響屁<br />\n個靚仔急急腳咁走撚左<br />\n呢個時候我先突然之間如夢初醒<br />\n立即跑去廁所度<br />\n但係我未撚除褲 啲屎已經放緊出嚟<br />\n放撚到我成條褲都係<br />\n結果我呢埋左係廁所<br />\n等到阿姐趕我走<br />\n我先借撚住條瀨屎褲行出去<br />\nP.s.<br />\n佢嘅微笑已經留喺我心裏面<br />\n但係我條褲嘅屎蹟都留起我條褲出面"},{"pid":"545850bf2b093178828eaa6133740d5bdb6b1d53","tid":804040,"uid":68725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"你FF完未"},{"pid":"0b091aa3cfdfac6450ee22d33f4206c073e0bcfb","tid":804040,"uid":653,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:39:07.000Z","msg":"155cm 75kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gi